name: CAS Symbiotic Armor
raw: ------------------------------ Ingredients ------------------------------ 2 pieces of Notum #L "Notum Fragment" "136624" or #L "Notum Chip" "136622" #L "Nano Programming Interface" "161699" #L "Inactive OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots" "164952" A Graft Armor part ( ie : #L "Flawless Graft Armor Boots" "142685" ) ------------------------------ Recipe ------------------------------ Nano Programming Interface + Inactive OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots = #L "Activated OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots" "164954" Skills: | NP,CH | ------------------------------ Notum piece + Activated OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots = #L "Stabilized OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots" "164956" Skills: | NP,CH | ------------------------------ Notum piece + Stabilized OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots = #L "Super-Stabilized OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots" "164958" Skills: | NP,CH | ------------------------------ Super-Stabilized OT Metamorphing Liquid Nanobots + Graft Armor = CAS Symbiotic Armor ( ie : #L "CAS Symbiotic Armor Boots" "165000" ) Skills: | NP,CH | ------------------------------ Comments ------------------------------ Popular Froob armor
